    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Tamás Nádasdy (Augsburg, 13 February 1551)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p>The news János Fejérthóy brought has turned out to be untrue. All of
                            Germania is at peace; the people of Magdeburg have lost hope, Maurice,
                            Electory of Saxony is attacking them. The Hungarians will get the
                            support. Oláh will be three days ahead of the King, who will leave 6-8
                            days later, together with Maximilian. Queen Mary will return to Flanders
                            straight after that, while the Emperor will stay here. Oláh presented
                            Ferenc Batthyány’s wife here on the 10<hi rend="super">th</hi>.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p>Spectabilis et Magnifice Domine et Frater Observandissime, servitiorum
                    meorum commendationem!</p>
                <p>Querelae et rumores, de quibus <persName>Feyerthoy</persName><note
                        type="critic">János Fejérthóy.</note> nomine Dominationis Vestrae Magnificae
                    locutus fuit, vanae sunt. Nihil eorum certum est. </p>
                <p>Tota Germaniae pars in quiete silet. Magdeburgenses quoque sunt in
                    desperatione. <persName>Mauritius</persName><note type="critic">Maurice, Elector
                        of Saxony.</note> dux arcta eos urget obsidione non paucis equitum et
                    peditum viribus speratum illorum itaque aut deditio aut expugnatio. Hic omnia ex
                    voto caesaris et regis confecta iam fere sunt, <add corresp="Olahus"
                        type="insert">subsidium habebitis</add>, affinitates adhuc secretae sunt.
                    Ego obtenta <del corresp="Olahus">ut</del> iam tandem venia praecedam <add
                        corresp="Olahus" type="insert">ad triduum</add>
                    <persName>maiestatem regiam</persName>, quae sexto vel octavo post die sequetur
                    cum <persName>Maximiliano</persName> rege. Serenissima regina
                        <persName>Maria</persName> statim post discessum regium revertetur in
                    Flandriam. <persName>Caesar</persName> hic aliquandiu manebit. Dominam
                        <persName>coniugem</persName><note type="critic">Katalin Svetkovics.</note>
                    domini <persName>Bothyany</persName><note type="critic">Ferenc Batthyány.</note>
                    cum honore 10. huius mensis die <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">huc</add>
                    introduci feci. De rebus omnibus <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert"
                    >aliis</add>, de quibus Dominatio Vestra ad me scripsit, non contemnendum
                    reporto responsum, de quo citavi plura. Dominatio Vestra cum domina
                        <persName>coniuge</persName><note type="critic">Orsolya Kanizsai.</note> sua
                    carissima, domina mea observandissima feliciter valeat.</p>
                <p>Ex <placeName>Augusta</placeName> 13. Februarii anno 1551.</p>
                <p>
                    <seg type="signature">Servitor Agriensis manu sua.</seg>
                </p>
                <p>Surculos regina exspectat.<note type="critic">See Ep. 757., and Ep.
                        761.</note><ref>/o:olahus.tei.15510106_1</ref><ref>/o:olahus.tei.15510127_1</ref></p>
                <pb/>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso">
